      </num>
      <head>
        Authority to act for the Chairperson.
      </head>
      <citation />
      <contents>
        <SECTNO>
          <aref type='CFR-TIC-SECT'>
            § 
            <subref title='7' part='3800' sect='4' psec='' tq='N'>
              3800.4
            </subref>
          </aref>
        </SECTNO>
        <SUBJECT>
          Authority to act for the Chairperson.
        </SUBJECT>
        <P>
          When the Chairperson is absent or temporarily unavailable, the Deputy
          Chairperson is authorized to act for the Chairperson.
        </P>
      </contents>
    </section>
